    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "problem_title",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 415,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "问题 1：Search 绕过 Datacenter 直连 MySQL（违反宪法）",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#ef4444",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "originalText": "问题 1：Search 绕过 Datacenter 直连 MySQL（违反宪法）",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "problem_detail_1",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 450,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "当前 Search 服务（vc2_search）直接连接 MySQL 查询 supplier_quotes 表。\n\n宪法规定：战略资产之间通过 API 接口通信，禁止共享数据库直连。\n\n正确做法：Search 应通过 Datacenter API 获取数据。",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "originalText": "当前 Search 服务（vc2_search）直接连接 MySQL 查询 supplier_quotes 表。\n\n宪法规定：战略资产之间通过 API 接口通信，禁止共享数据库直连。\n\n正确做法：Search 应通过 Datacenter API 获取数据。",
      "autoResize": true
    },

    {
