    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "solution_title",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 635,
      "width": 1080,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "改造方案：修复数据流 + 新建 Search UI",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#15803d",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "originalText": "改造方案：修复数据流 + 新建 Search UI",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "solution_detail",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 670,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "① Datacenter 新增 /api/v1/search 端点\n   返回脱敏后的报价数据（无 supplier_id、无成本价）\n\n② Search 改造为调用 Datacenter API\n   搜索逻辑从 MySQL 查询改为调 Datacenter\n\n③ 删除 Datacenter 的采购推荐接口\n   /procure/recommend 和 /procure/compare",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "originalText": "① Datacenter 新增 /api/v1/search 端点\n   返回脱敏后的报价数据（无 supplier_id、无成本价）\n\n② Search 改造为调用 Datacenter API\n   搜索逻辑从 MySQL 查询改为调 Datacenter\n\n③ 删除 Datacenter 的采购推荐接口\n   /procure/recommend 和 /procure/compare",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "solution_detail_2",
      "x": 640,
      "y": 670,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "④ Search UI 前端（待建设）\n   新建 Next.js 应用，搜索框居中 + 卡片展示\n   语音搜索 + 企微联系供应商（占位符）\n   端口 3003，search.ibotclaw.com 访问\n\n⑤ 正确数据流\n   Pipeline -> MySQL -> Datacenter(API) ->\n   Search(AI增强) -> Search UI(前端)",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "originalText": "④ Search UI 前端（待建设）\n   新建 Next.js 应用，搜索框居中 + 卡片展示\n   语音搜索 + 企微联系供应商（占位符）\n   端口 3003，search.ibotclaw.com 访问\n\n⑤ 正确数据流\n   Pipeline -> MySQL -> Datacenter(API) ->\n   Search(AI增强) -> Search UI(前端)",
      "autoResize": true
    },

